# SVG Icon System

## Icon Categories & Size Scale

| Category | Tailwind Class | Pixel Size | ViewBox | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Nav (L1 Sidebar) | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Sidebar navigation icons |
| L2 Submenu | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Submenu item icons |
| UI Actions | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Buttons, toolbars, utility icons |
| Product Illustration | `size-10` | 40×40 | `0 0 32 32` | Device/service card icons (Card Machine, Sound Box) |
| Inline Small | `size-4` | 16×16 | `0 0 24 24` | Chevrons inside rows, status indicators |
| Promo/Feature | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Feature cards (Connect Plus) |

## Color Patterns

### 1. `currentColor` Inheritance (REQUIRED for all new icons)
All SVG icons MUST use `currentColor` instead of hardcoded color values. This allows the parent element to control the icon color via Tailwind `text-[color]`.

```tsx
// CORRECT — inherits color from parent
<path stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" />
<path fill="white" />  /* body/background fills use literal white */

// WRONG — hardcoded colors break theming
<path stroke="#004299" fill="#004299" />
<path stroke="#00b8f5" fill="#00b8f5" />
<path stroke="#101010" fill="#101010" />
```

### 2. Duo-Tone Pattern (All Product & Feature Icons)
All illustration icons (Card Machine, Sound Box, EMI, AMC, Connect Plus, etc.) use a two-tone system:
- **Body/background shapes**: `fill="white"` — light fill for the main shape
- **Detail strokes & fills**: `stroke="currentColor"` / `fill="currentColor"` — inherits from parent
- **Resolved detail color**: `#101010` (Foreground) — the same dark color used by sidebar icons
- The icon container does NOT set a `text-[color]` class; icons inherit the default `#101010` foreground

```tsx
<div className="size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd] flex items-center justify-center">
  <CardMachineIcon />
</div>
```

### 3. Sidebar Icon Pattern
Sidebar icons follow the same `#101010` foreground with `white` body fills:
- Stroke/fill details: `stroke="currentColor"` / `fill="currentColor"` → inherits `#101010`
- Background shapes: `fill="white"`
- Size: `size-6`, viewBox varies per icon

### 4. UI/Action Icon Pattern (Icons.tsx library)
Simple outline icons using only `currentColor`:
- `stroke="currentColor"` with `strokeWidth="2"`
- `fill="none"` (outline only) or `fill="currentColor"` (filled variants)
- Accept `className` prop with default `"size-6"`

## SVG Component Structure

### Standard Props Interface
```tsx
interface IconProps {
  className?: string;
}

function MyIcon({ className = "size-6" }: IconProps) {
  return (
    <svg className={className} viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
      {/* paths */}
    </svg>
  );
}
```

### Product Icon Structure (32×32 viewBox)
```tsx
function ProductIcon() {
  return (
    <svg className="size-10" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none">
      <path d="..." fill="white" />                    {/* body fill */}
      <path d="..." stroke="currentColor" />            {/* outline */}
      <path d="..." fill="currentColor" />              {/* detail fills */}
    </svg>
  );
}
```

